OL,4,G0335FThe Doors: Live At The Bowl `68
OL,5,     GAt the height of their musical
OL,6,     Gprowess, The Doors perform all
OL,7,     Gtheir classic hits during their
OL,8,     Glegendary 1968 concert at the
OL,9,     GHollywood Bowl.
OL,10,G0505FDiscovering: The Mamas & The Papas
OL,11,     GA fascinating look at The Mamas
OL,12,     Gand The Papas, the American folk
OL,13,     Grock group whose easygoing vocal
OL,14,     Gharmonies provided the soundtrack
OL,15,     Gto the late 60s.
OL,16,G0535FDiscovering: James Brown
OL,17,     GA fascinating look at the life
OL,18,     Gand career of James Brown. Dubbed
OL,19,     G'the Godfather of Soul', he was
OL,20,     Gone of the most iconic figures in
OL,21,     Gmusic up until his death in 2006.
